        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Like social tokens,
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUEuOhSAQPM1jaQBBZcFiNnMNg9BPiQgGmpl4--HpYpJOOt2VSn2sQVhTvvSZCpJaIM_eaTbwqZdCEaeFY5OciC_zOwMcxgeNuQI56xK8NehTvBmUckk2DVTRXsBke6oscKaotWpyi3ASxkVx8tGZTXUeogUNP5CvFIEEvSGe5dV_vfh3m7fx-fARO5vaRbzmlFPGmGK97OnYsc6UMAKv_Iz7S9Bj5V2pS0Fj98Y5SNYx4ZKyj2uD980cEG6gGZ_bPmr0eM0QzRLAPZnwaeG2iNcJOsJvCYAI-Xl-gk7jMEghSVNzqfUR_4X-AAOVcZY" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Fairmint
         </a>
         is built on DeFi rails, but unlike them, you wouldn\xe2\x80\x99t know that from looking at their site. DeFi is part of Fairmint\xe2\x80\x99s tech stack, not its main value prop.
        </p>
        <h3 style="color: #1a1a1a; font-family: 'SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 1.375em; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;">
         <strong>
          Meet Fairmint
         </strong>
        </h3>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Fairmint is like Kickstarter on steroids, mixed with Carta, embedded right in the products we use and love. They\xe2\x80\x99re building the picks and shovels for founders to turn their equity into the most powerful tool to engage with their contributors.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Equity powers the entire stack of entrepreneurship and is the most powerful tool to align financial interests. It has a simple value prop: help make this company more valuable, and you will be rewarded. Equity is the reason startups can write that bullet that goes something like...
        </p>
        <ul style="margin: 1em 0;">
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            Be a team player.
           </strong>
           Be willing to get your hands dirty, go above and beyond the responsibilities of your role, and do whatever it takes to help this company reach its full potential!
          </p>
         </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         ...on every job description, with a straight face.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         It is also the greatest wealth-building financial instrument. Until now, the absence of a single, global, open, and interoperable system of record for equity has hampered innovation and the democratization of equity ownership.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Luckily, global, open, and interoperable systems of record are what crypto does best, and Fairmint is using it to build \xe2\x80\x9csoftware-powered financing services to raise capital continuously from anyone who supports their product and mission.\xe2\x80\x9d
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Fairmint created the
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUM2O8yAMfJpyS8RvSw8c9vK9RgTESVETkw_MrvL2S9vDSpYse-wZe6InWHM53ZErsVahTGl24iqtMvrOZqdnYY1lqU5LAdh92hyVBuxoYUvRU8r43uBcGvZw3HvNZdB2iepuuNYCgrKdT0UbrNXspTP5NifACA6-oZwZgW3uQXTUi_q6yH89Fp_KnpDGmHsV_QJDzEgJW2518OvrFkAallyGpVErMMD_lujs0yw5ySUXQtyFMorfRjH6ut1ANnng86L5vsqxtlDJx2dX2FlxmCnkknDt8PPhd9jeQH9z6nlv2LknQB82mD8O0Mez90N0HuAQfuoGRFA-zZct9na9Gm1YV5tzdw__hH4BW2aClQ" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Continuous Agreement for Future Equity
         </a>
         (CAFE), an updated version of Y Combinator\xe2\x80\x99s
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMuOwyAM_JpyjHgm6YHDXvobEQ-3RSUQgdkof78kPaxkydaM7PGMMwivXA695YqkVShL8JqNfBZK3onX0rNZzSTU5VkAVhOixtKAbM3G4AyGnK4NSrkib83FcwQprFNsEnzmILmV9g6KUsqksuTUWUzzAZIDDb9QjpyARP1G3OpN_Nz4o9e-78Ph8mpDMpjL0MeO-uzaCglrn0nQnHLKGLszoQSdBjaYGifgjW_pc5N0ffGhNlvRuM95gBSdMtpcQnp1-vM2K8SL6GaW3teWAh4LJGMj-K9P_CZzvY3HBjrBXiMgQvmCp_l5GkclFelqPveM0r_QHxIQeKo" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          SAFE
         </a>
         , which lets a company\xe2\x80\x99s stakeholders buy or earn equity in the company, at any time, directly from their website. It\xe2\x80\x99s \xe2\x80\x9cprogrammable equity.\xe2\x80\x9d Companies will be able to add an \xe2\x80\x9cInvest\xe2\x80\x9d button right to their site as easily as they add a \xe2\x80\x9cBuy with Apple Pay\xe2\x80\x9d button today.
        </p>
